name: Outer Light
description:
beacons of light at night,
dark night
I try to walk, but that light doesn't let me
it's not a normal light, i don't know what it is
but this light multiplies,
spreads,
intensifies
it takes all my problems
and makes me stop
surprised
unable to react
Nevertheless
I feel like that light embraces me
and it makes me feel calm, quiet
almost like I'm on top of something
with so much power
I accept it
because who doesn't like power?
